{"tid":1426704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被港人淡忘 只讀不貢獻的維基百科","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:55:17.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55a28a666b12bc1d944dea9080b454ff7d2adbfe","tid":1426704,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"話說近期就反送中的文宣之中，維基百科完全被港人淡忘。香港的媒體也無視維基的存在。而不論英文或中文維基百科，大陸的力量亦非常強大。有外媒就近期的風波進行了報導，而且是訪問維基百科的編輯者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登亦有人希望大家能幫忙，幫手編輯和增加有關反條例嘅條目。不過反應非常冷淡。</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1421147/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1421147/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTemplate%3A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=dbb5a31d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n報導指<span style=\"color: red;\">根據中文維基百科，屬香港人的編輯只有18.8%，比例非常少。而大陸那些編輯的人不會寫中國政治，只會寫有利於中國政府的內容。6月15日的期死去的抗議者梁振傑的條目，不久亦以關注度不足亦被刪除。</span><br />\n<br />\n他們的恐懼並非沒有根據。在過去幾年中，中國政府不僅禁止維基百科，還鼓勵創建替代維基和在線百科全書，百度百科以填補空白。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wired.co.uk/article/hong-kong-protests-wikipedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fhong-kong-protests-wikipedia&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=c763710c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.co.uk/article/hong-kong-protests-wikipedia</a>"},{"pid":"082b108d6062d0890ea7331b5dd7edd54c594ddf","tid":1426704,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d89809abe8361ce742086fb4d9824b45ac18fa4e","tid":1426704,"uid":162090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:55:17.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n但可唔可以打啱人地個名？<br />\n義士叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">梁凌杰</span></span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}